node.text: The four 19 year-olds featured in the new documentary, Rebuilding Hope: The Children of 9/11 — Jamie Gartenberg Pila, Gabriel Jacobs Dick, Ronald Milam Jr., and Alexa Smagala — are opening up about being born after losing their fathers during the September 11th terrorist attacks, how they’ve found inspiration in the fathers they never met, and how they’ve tried to honor them in their daily lives. 🙏

node.text: Stephen Curry is still pinching himself that he scored wife Ayesha Curry. ❤️ The Golden State Warriors champion gushed about Ayesha while chatting with PEOPLE (the TV Show!) about their foundation Eat.Learn.Play, which offers food and educational resources to low-income families in Oakland, California. "We just celebrated 10 years of marriage," the athlete said. "Her heart for service is a big reason why we've been able to do the things that we get to do." 🙏 Tap the bio link for more. | #Regram @ayeshacurry
